{"tid":29658,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"無勁小說家是否其中一個原因 令香港電影停滯不前？","createTime":"2016-12-08T16:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T04:29:53.000Z","uid":59441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ecf1a1a83f2f7ee2db161e6f751eddbd918446b","tid":29658,"uid":59441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T16:47:29.000Z","msg":"其實外國好多出色電影都由小說改編 好似教父 月黑高飛 阿甘正傳 閃靈 捉智雙雄⋯⋯⋯⋯仲有好多<br />\n<br />\n單計Stephen King嘅小說改編 而又成為很高評的電影也不少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實如果香港有多啲勁小說家 再用其作品改編 會否使香港電影業界帶來希望？<br />\n<br />\n當然香港電影並非這單一原因 使其發展停滯不前 這只是一個粗淺諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不喜勿插<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5e82f59800d0e9974889eea14360e5bc55bf0e","tid":29658,"uid":34383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:03:33.000Z","msg":"敢正正經經拍套衛斯理先啦"},{"pid":"0d86706ce18833d352e9f86b0472f61c0c7caea7","tid":29658,"uid":34872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:40:27.000Z","msg":"冇好既編劇重要d <br />\n橋段就套套都差唔多 睇佢點鋪排得好好睇睇<br />\n睇得太多電影 好易估到d劇情 其實都幾無引<br />\n利申:9up"},{"pid":"d81780d5a5d47e51ab8a619accaa143512af1a47","tid":29658,"uid":43751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:41:50.000Z","msg":"我又唔撚明<br />\n金古小說咁撚勁<br />\n又食正俠武條女<br />\n但又發唔起圍"},{"pid":"2d280716a895c104a7830ba25e5ea9b51762319b","tid":29658,"uid":59830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T17:54:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a41a4d45f98598b3ffaf9ad5b56e29c921674621","tid":29658,"uid":11185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T19:34:34.000Z","msg":"荷里活電影公司可以投資落去小說度／特意培養小說家<br />\n香港？想搵個人睇書都難"},{"pid":"330f6ad93ad78150c90b5062ef1a8fd154af79bd","tid":29658,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T19:45:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實香港寫小說真係乞食 所以少作家出現<br />\n利申:志願係長篇小說作家 30歲前做唔到準備係ifc跳落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 考埋個dse就準備訓身寫作</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前都好似你咁好鐘意寫野<br />\n靈感一黎可以通宵寫萬幾字<br />\n但係依家成日對住字對到好想嘔<br />\n除左論文之外已經好耐冇寫小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf13218750b7601fa38e7d3df372c4c351e4a47","tid":29658,"uid":28960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T19:48:01.000Z","msg":"依到都大把高質小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba6e2b184e277f94b9e2f3582970b5a909eeaf3b","tid":29658,"uid":42848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T20:25:38.000Z","msg":"有好劇本無好導演執行都會扣好多分,<br />\n就算stephen king啲小說改編電影都有唔少大伏,<br />\n始終將小說轉變成電影既過程同單憑小說想像都已經好唔同"},{"pid":"220a5eecc48c8fd539e0255ab66b975f9198e51e","tid":29658,"uid":33734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T21:54:49.000Z","msg":"西營盤就準備拍真人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即管睇下結果係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4408b2ec8b2df3e68d3a5f928aadd783d1b10a","tid":29658,"uid":17335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T22:02:06.000Z","msg":"李碧華好多改編<br />\n霸王別姬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be38a258970e939f1a8e7f307a18de28e6f8fdf9","tid":29658,"uid":4260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T22:02:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有好劇本無好導演執行都會扣好多分,<br />\n就算stephen king啲小說改編電影都有唔少大伏,<br />\n始終將小說轉變成電影既過程同單憑小說想像都已經好唔同</blockquote><br />\nExactly <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1681d8b59917161e6e9e89160c8131190a0bdcc6","tid":29658,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T22:05:12.000Z","msg":"其實唔係冇勁既小説家，但全部行純文學路線不適宜改做電影。<br />\n<br />\n同埋都唔係冇小説改篇電影，紅Van咪係囉"},{"pid":"98f9a3864eea4